name: Great Bear (Electric Coffin X Phosphene)
description: Electric Coffin is a Seattle based collaborative artist group, founded by Stefan Hofmann and Duffy De Armas, exploring the intersection of art and commerce.  “Great Bear” is a timed release starting May 5 @ 8:00 am PT and ending 24 hours later at 8:00 pm PT. All unsold editions will be burned.
